{"version":"NotebookV1","origId":4289645842581566,"name":"05.Results transformation","language":"python","commands":[{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7216504859341992,"guid":"9ae068cf-6524-4049-aa13-5fe6a7bd1545","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":100.0,"command":"%md\n# Transform Results Data\nThis process transforms raw data from the **Bronze** layer and prepares it for analytical use in the **Silver** layer by applying the following steps:\n\n1. **Read data** from the bronze `results` table.\n2. **Filter out rows** where primary identifying relationships are null (such as `driverId`, `constructorId`, or `raceName`) to maintain relational integrity.\n3. **Remove duplicate** records based on unique outcome identifiers.\n4. **Select relevant columns** required for downstream BI metrics, dropping unnecessary columns (such as `url`).\n5. **Standardize column names** using `snake_case` (e.g., converting `constructorId` to `constructor_id`, `driverId` to `driver_id`, `positionText` to `position_text`).\n6. **Cast data types** to proper numerical structures for quantitative analysis (e.g., ensuring `grid`, `laps`, `position`, and `points` are numeric formats rather than plain strings).\n7. **Transform text values** for columns like `status` and `position_text` into standard standardized categories.\n8. **Write the transformed data** to the silver `results` table.","commandVersion":0,"state":"input","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"dd816b35-349f-46e0-ba61-92bead85275e"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7216504859341993,"guid":"ac15ff0a-98a7-4ad0-805c-7f08a87573bf","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":200.0,"command":"%run\n../00-common/01.envirmonet-config","commandVersion":0,"state":"input","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"eb68793e-e626-4cc6-a2ac-bbb8b679be3a"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7216504859341994,"guid":"34a34dd9-5515-4e99-8f6c-5cb159f05858","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":300.0,"command":"file_name = 'results'\nbronze_table = f'{catalog}.{bronze_schema}.{file_name}'\nsilver_table = f'{catalog}.{silver_schema}.{file_name}'","commandVersion":0,"state":"input","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"19b4137a-45e4-4d2b-9021-0d5456c58b5a"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7216504859341995,"guid":"36a28a1f-48a2-4cb0-9653-b0f2edfcfa01","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":400.0,"command":"results_df = spark.read.table(bronze_table)\ndisplay(results_df)","commandVersion":0,"state":"input","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":